---
// About page for Black Living
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title='關於黑哥 - Black Living 黑哥家居品牌故事'
  description='了解Black Living黑哥家居的品牌故事，從黑標王到專業居家生活品牌的發展歷程，以及我們對品質與服務的承諾。'
  type='website'
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class='py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-black text-white'>
    <div class='container mx-auto px-4 text-center'>
      <h1 class='text-5xl font-bold mb-6'>關於 Black Living 黑哥家居</h1>
      <p class='text-xl opacity-90 max-w-3xl mx-auto'>
        從專營席夢思「黑標」床墊的小店，到成為客戶信賴的居家生活品牌
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Brand Story -->
  <section class='py-16 bg-white'>
    <div class='container mx-auto px-4'>
      <div class='max-w-4xl mx-auto'>
        <h2 class='text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12'>品牌故事</h2>

        <div class='space-y-8'>
          <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center'>
            <div>
              <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>從「黑標王」起家</h3>
              <p class='text-gray-600 leading-relaxed'>
                我們的故事始於對席夢思「黑標」床墊的專業與熱忱。最初以「黑標王」為名，
                專注於提供最優質的席夢思黑標系列產品，憑藉對品質的堅持與對客戶需求的深度了解，
                逐漸在業界建立起良好的口碑。
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class='text-center'>
              <div class='text-6xl mb-4'>🏆</div>
              <p class='text-gray-500'>蝦皮第一賣家</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center'>
            <div class='order-2 md:order-1 text-center'>
              <div class='text-6xl mb-4'>🌟</div>
              <p class='text-gray-500'>百位網友五星好評</p>
            </div>
            <div class='order-1 md:order-2'>
              <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>品質與服務的承諾</h3>
              <p class='text-gray-600 leading-relaxed'>
                「四大堅持」是我們的核心價值：全台價格最低、專業黑標銷售、正派公司經營、客服即時回覆。
                這不僅是我們的承諾，更是每一位客戶選擇我們的理由。我們相信，
                只有真正將客戶需求放在第一位，才能贏得長久的信任。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center'>
            <div>
              <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>轉型為 Black Living</h3>
              <p class='text-gray-600 leading-relaxed'>
                隨著客戶需求的多元化，我們將品牌升級為「Black Living 黑哥家居」，
                服務範圍從單一的床墊銷售擴展至整個居家生活領域。Logo中的黑色代表我們的起源，
                月亮象徵全天候不間斷的服務，Living則體現我們對美好居家生活的追求。
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class='text-center'>
              <div class='flex justify-center items-center space-x-4 text-4xl mb-4'>
                <span>🖤</span>
                <span>🌙</span>
                <span>🏠</span>
              </div>
              <p class='text-gray-500'>Black • Moon • Living</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Four Commitments -->
  <section class='py-16 bg-gray-50'>
    <div class='container mx-auto px-4'>
      <h2 class='text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12'>四大堅持</h2>

      <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8'>
        <div class='text-center bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md'>
          <div class='text-4xl mb-4'>💰</div>
          <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-3'>#全台價格最低</h3>
          <p class='text-gray-600 text-sm'>專櫃價2-3折起，買貴退差價保證</p>
        </div>

        <div class='text-center bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md'>
          <div class='text-4xl mb-4'>🎯</div>
          <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-3'>#專業黑標銷售</h3>
          <p class='text-gray-600 text-sm'>專精席夢思黑標，提供專業諮詢</p>
        </div>

        <div class='text-center bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md'>
          <div class='text-4xl mb-4'>🏢</div>
          <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-3'>#正派公司經營</h3>
          <p class='text-gray-600 text-sm'>合法登記，誠信經營，品質保證</p>
        </div>

        <div class='text-center bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md'>
          <div class='text-4xl mb-4'>⚡</div>
          <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold mb-3'>#客服即時回覆</h3>
          <p class='text-gray-600 text-sm'>Line官方帳號快速響應客戶需求</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Physical Stores -->
  <section class='py-16 bg-white'>
    <div class='container mx-auto px-4'>
      <h2 class='text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12'>實體展間</h2>

      <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8'>
        <!-- Zhonghe Store -->
        <div class='bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg'>
          <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>中和展間</h3>
          <div class='space-y-3 text-gray-600'>
            <div class='flex items-center'>
              <span class='w-6'>📍</span>
              <span>新北市中和區 [詳細地址待提供]</span>
            </div>
            <div class='flex items-center'>
              <span class='w-6'>🕒</span>
              <span>營業時間：週一至週日 09:00-21:00</span>
            </div>
            <div class='flex items-center'>
              <span class='w-6'>🚗</span>
              <span>備有停車位，交通便利</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a
            href='/appointment?store=zhonghe'
            class='mt-6 inline-block bg-black text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors'
          >
            預約中和試躺
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Zhongli Store -->
        <div class='bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg'>
          <h3 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>中壢展間</h3>
          <div class='space-y-3 text-gray-600'>
            <div class='flex items-center'>
              <span class='w-6'>📍</span>
              <span>桃園市中壢區 [詳細地址待提供]</span>
            </div>
            <div class='flex items-center'>
              <span class='w-6'>🕒</span>
              <span>營業時間：週一至週日 09:00-21:00</span>
            </div>
            <div class='flex items-center'>
              <span class='w-6'>🚗</span>
              <span>備有停車位，交通便利</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a
            href='/appointment?store=zhongli'
            class='mt-6 inline-block bg-black text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors'
          >
            預約中壢試躺
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class='py-16 bg-black text-white'>
    <div class='container mx-auto px-4 text-center'>
      <h2 class='text-3xl font-bold mb-6'>開始您的優質睡眠之旅</h2>
      <p class='text-xl mb-8 text-gray-300'>歡迎透過Line與我們聯繫，或直接預約門市試躺體驗</p>

      <div class='flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center'>
        <a
          href='https://line.me/R/ti/p/@blackking'
          target='_blank'
          rel='noopener noreferrer'
          class='bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-3 font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors'
        >
          Line 線上諮詢
        </a>
        <a
          href='/appointment'
          class='bg-white text-black px-8 py-3 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors'
        >
          預約門市試躺
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
